It’s just so hard to explain to people.
Most people really just don’t know what to make of it the first time they see it.
Usually you don't see her until her cloud of darkness has already enveloped you.
When she is either really hungry or really excited, it can go hundreds of meters. 
If you see something that looks like a really dark cloud but it’s on the ground, move in the other direction.
Right angles might help, but that’s assuming she doesn’t come your way.
Otherwise you gotta hide under something.
I don’t really have practical fighting advice.
She’s pretty easy for me with the right charm.
But it takes special shrine training to learn how to use one.